trans-unit.source: Authentication credentials could not be found.
Authentication request could not be processed due to a system problem.
trans-unit.target: Tizimdagi muammo tufayli autentifikatsiya so'rovi bajarilmadi.

trans-unit.source: Cookie has already been used by someone else.
Not privileged to request the resource.
trans-unit.target: Sizda ushbu manbani talab qilishga ruxsat yo'q..

trans-unit.source: No authentication provider found to support the authentication token.
trans-unit.target: Haqiqiylikni tasdiqlovchi belgini qo'llab-quvvatlovchi biron bir autentifikatsiya provayderi topilmadi.

trans-unit.source: No session available, it either timed out or cookies are not enabled.
trans-unit.target: Sessiya topilmadi, muddati tugamadi yoki cookie-fayllar yoqilmagan.

trans-unit.source: Too many failed login attempts, please try again later.
trans-unit.target: Kirish urinishlari muvaffaqiyatsiz tugadi, keyinroq qayta urinib ko'ring.
Kirish havolasi yaroqsiz yoki muddati tugagan.

trans-unit.source: Too many failed login attempts, please try again in %minutes% minute.
trans-unit.target: Kirish uchun muvaffaqiyatsiz urinishlar, %minutes% daqiqadan so'ng qayta urinib ko'ring.

trans-unit.source: Too many failed login attempts, please try again in %minutes% minutes.
trans-unit.target: Koʻplab muvaffaqiyatsiz kirish urinishlari, iltimos, %minutes% daqiqadan so'ng qayta urinib koʻring.|Koʻplab muvaffaqiyatsiz kirish urinishlari, iltimos, %minutes% daqiqadan so'ng qayta urinib koʻring.
